[{"short_id":"839cni","created_at":"2026-03-13T13:47:18.000-05:00","title":"Crude proposal of page for viewing invitees activity","url":"","score":1,"flags":0,"comment_count":1,"description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/lobsters/lobsters/issues/1949\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003eThis issue\u003c/a\u003e was oppened recently by \u003ca href=\"https://lobste.rs/~technomancy\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003e@technomancy\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://lobste.rs/~jmiven\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003e@jmiven\u003c/a\u003e. Thinking about how it could look to be the most helpful and came here to gather suggestions.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAn early crude layout:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://imgur.com/a/DNsVpmO\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003eFrom where to access it\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eview activity redirects to the page\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eusername of invitee redirects to their profile\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://imgur.com/a/LLceojo\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003eVery crude looks of the page\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ethe \"n comments\" by the side of the user name should link to a page showing their recent comments. The \"n posts\" as well.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eUnclear points:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWould it be better to just display the comments after all?\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWhat info about users should be displayed and how to lay it out?\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWhat about invitees' invitees ? How to display this info? Should it?\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHow to sort this list of users?\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://lobste.rs/~veqq\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003e@veqq\u003c/a\u003e was very helpful to this early layout, thanks :)\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"[This issue](https://github.com/lobsters/lobsters/issues/1949) was oppened recently by @technomancy and @jmiven. Thinking about how it could look to be the most helpful and came here to gather suggestions.\r\n\r\nAn early crude layout:\r\n\r\n[From where to access it](https://imgur.com/a/DNsVpmO)\r\n- view activity redirects to the page\r\n- username of invitee redirects to their profile\r\n\r\n[Very crude looks of the page](https://imgur.com/a/LLceojo) \r\n- the \"n comments\" by the side of the user name should link to a page showing their recent comments. The \"n posts\" as well.\r\n\r\nUnclear points:\r\n- Would it be better to just display the comments after all?\r\n- What info about users should be displayed and how to lay it out?\r\n- What about invitees' invitees ? How to display this info? Should it?\r\n- How to sort this list of users?\r\n\r\n@veqq was very helpful to this early layout, thanks :)","submitter_user":"rebeca","user_is_author":true,"tags":["ask","meta"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/839cni","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/839cni/crude_proposal_page_for_viewing_invitees"},{"short_id":"rya8rs","created_at":"2026-03-13T13:44:22.000-05:00","title":"Marknote 1.5 released for KDE","url":"https://blogs.kde.org/2026/03/13/marknote-1.5/","score":1,"flags":0,"comment_count":0,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"raymii","user_is_author":false,"tags":["linux","release"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/rya8rs","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/rya8rs/marknote_1_5_released_for_kde"},{"short_id":"btf0gu","created_at":"2026-03-13T12:19:11.000-05:00","title":"Software Bonkers","url":"https://craigmod.com/essays/software_bonkers/","score":2,"flags":0,"comment_count":0,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"jefftriplett","user_is_author":false,"tags":["vibecoding"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/btf0gu","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/btf0gu/software_bonkers"},{"short_id":"dm1j3a","created_at":"2026-03-13T10:49:15.000-05:00","title":"OpenClaw and the Dream of Free Labour","url":"https://entropy